Package com.rb.nonbiz.text

Class SimpleHumanReadableLabel

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.text.SimpleHumanReadableLabel
All Implemented Interfaces:
HumanReadableLabel
public class SimpleHumanReadableLabel
extends java.lang.Object
implements HumanReadableLabel
A human-readable label used to document our output. It's a simple implementation of HumanReadableLabel.

We never use labels in our business logic; they exist only for explanatory purposes. In other words, only humans are supposed to read a HumanReadableLabel.
